    <title>虚拟机简易安装教程</title>
    <link href="/2021/10/09/%E4%BF%9D%E5%A7%86%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA/"/>
    <url>/2021/10/09/%E4%BF%9D%E5%A7%86%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>虚拟机安装过程：</strong></p><p>1）准备Ubuntu或者centOs系统镜像（推荐官网获取：<a href="https://ubuntu.com/">ubuntu</a> <a href="https://www.centos.org/download/">centOs</a>）</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/4NnqkxTY8ZBIuvc.png" alt="image-20211009205914751"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/P6ptbqDS4FVAEwH.png" alt="image-20211009205817030"></p><p>2)下载好镜像，打开VMware点击创建新的虚拟机</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/wYQJfl7XiezHySN.png" alt="image-20211009205725116"></p><p>3）跟着引导操作</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/j5heDdCBmJ9EAFR.png" alt="image-20211009210008134"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/wO9UvFHjS1asmBh.png" alt="image-20211009210052050"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/JvSge72Vfj4R8mG.png" alt="image-20211009210117821"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/1QfXjFTOCtqySgo.png" alt="image-20211009210225262"></p><center>这里建议选择30G</center><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/PGe1Ho6nyq4N3bA.png" alt="image-20211009210540500"></p><p>4）等待虚拟机安装，这里选择Install CentOS 7</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/vibKYRc9HCtSkUV.png" alt="image-20211009210758320"></p><p>5)选择语言</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/ihsxStwBoD8GU6v.png" alt="image-20211009210653252"></p><p>6)选择一下系统设置</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/gQaljiVSPBpGzfM.png" alt="image-20211009211138613"></p><p>7)配置一下root用户，然后等待安装完成，需要注意的是，如果你的密码安全等级不够高，需要点击两下完成</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/10/09/qhDNZKB7daE6fJ9.png" alt="image-20211009211251254"></p><p>8)等待安装完成后点击一下重启就大功告成拉！</p>]]></content>
    
    
